{"tid":517593,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"免費教unity (C#) ~2 含YouTube channel","createTime":"2018-01-02T12:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T16:12:55.000Z","uid":145737,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d24df331b532851619b49dc200a0c047dd11179a","tid":517593,"uid":145737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"由零開始製造MMORPG <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一課:<br />\n    1. 角色移動<br />\n    2. 控制鏡頭(Camera)距離, 旋轉<br />\n    3. 移動動作, 效果<br />\n<br />\n第二課:<br />\n    1. 角色屬性狀態<br />\n    2. 文檔讀取資料<br />\n    3. 背包系統<br />\n    4. NPC對話 (購買物品, 任務對話框)<br />\n<br />\n第三課:<br />\n    1. Program生成GameObject (怪物)<br />\n    2. 控制怪物屬性狀態, 物品金錢掉落<br />\n    3. 任務系統<br />\n<br />\n第四課:<br />\n   1. 網絡編程(TCP/IP)<br />\n   2. 同步角色資料到資料庫<br />\n   3. 同步所有玩家position, rotation, animation<br />\n   4. 交易系統<br />\n   5. 對話系統<br />\n<br />\n教學片將會慢慢upload 請各位巴絲耐心等候<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b1cNCqa18PY&amp;list=PLbuSWYNGBHxfumrAf7mVn6v1260AFwU5v&amp;index=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Db1cNCqa18PY%26list%3DPLbuSWYNGBHxfumrAf7mVn6v1260AFwU5v%26index%3D1&d=MpJNZB9Gooef3DL4O5ImK2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ed76c979\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=b1cNCqa18PY&amp;list=PLbuSWYNGBHxfumrAf7mVn6v1260AFwU5v&amp;index=1</a><br />\n<br />\nTelegram Group:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FOfTkRDUpe5yVqZMjwHUfQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFOfTkRDUpe5yVqZMjwHUfQ&d=MpJNZB9Gooef3DL4O5ImK2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=6cd84800\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FOfTkRDUpe5yVqZMjwHUfQ</a>"},{"pid":"f0ac039e2ce60e7d8524a3e577e63fad58676db6","tid":517593,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T12:44:56.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50